Christian RASMUSSEN, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 84. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Nov. 4, 1935. Gazan & Caldwell and Simone Gazan, all of New York City, for appellant. Leo J. Hickey, U. S. Atty., of Brooklyn, N. Y., and Tompkins, Boal & Tompkins, of New York City (Arthur M. Boal, of New York City, of counsel), for the United States.

*1008Before L. HAND, SWAN, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed.
